data.description:
If you're in the market for a new home, you don't want to miss this beautiful Fort Mill Town Home located at 116 Jason Ct. This home features 2 bed 1.5 bath in this growing city. Enjoy the spacious fenced in back yard or have a relaxing morning coffee on your front patio. Hot summer day ? Get your tan on near your community pool which is within walking distance ! Explore the scenic Anne Springs Close Greenway, only a short distance away from this beautiful Fort Mill townhome. Enjoy hiking, biking, and much more!

This home is situated in a quiet and friendly neighborhood, providing a peaceful and relaxing atmosphere. This location offers easy access to nearby shops, restaurants, and other amenities, making it the perfect place for those who want to be close to everything.
